description: Erection of a part 6 and part 7 storey building to provide 99 private and 25 affordable residential units, commercial/retail space on Copenhagen Street, community hall and library at ground level and a basement providing 16 car parking spaces and bicycle storage space.
decision_conditions:
CONDITION:  No part of the development shall commence until details of the improvements and alteration works including all necessary traffic safety measures required to the public highways, footways and streetscape including street planting has been approved by the Local Planning Authority in writing.

REASON:  In order that the Local Planning Authority is satisfied with the details of the proposal.
